This project tries to give you a simple way to validate HTML forms. The core API only depends on native Javascript, but plugins can be used to further enhance its power.

Useful links : 
* Website : http://ippontech.github.io/JSV_API
* Wiki : https://github.com/ippontech/JSV_API/wiki
* Latest JS file version : https://github.com/ippontech/JSV_API/tree/master/core/build/js
